{"tid":1471800,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"荃灣811有市民/示威者俾白衫佬斬到咁撚樣，付國豪瘀少少咪撚出嚟獻世","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:07:47.000Z","uid":36008,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"74219496240f6adc0cff0215482d0b0ffb61b67b","tid":1471800,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"【1900】有已核實身分的醫護人員聯絡本頻道，提供兩張荃灣被斬示威者（圖）送院時傷勢的照片。<br />\n<br />\n該名醫護呼籲，希望市民認清什麼才是真正的暴力，又稱不會指責昨晚在機場集會動手的示威者，因為兩個月以來不少示威者都被警察或者黑社會攻擊致受傷，而傷勢之重，與昨日於機場被打的疑似公安及環時記者根本無從比較，「好多人已經為呢件事付出好多，現在唔係指責或者割席嘅時候」。<br />\n<br />\n以下為傷勢照片，或會引起嚴重不安，查看前請務必做好心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n左腳傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k1UL0.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3WrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=cc155008\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg</a><br />\n右手傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeH3751.jpg&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3WrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=84851614\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6e5AZis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6e5AZis.jpg&h=f213e2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews/1405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantiextraditionverifiednews%2F1405&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3WrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=6d6a3ead\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews/1405</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有自69以嚟大量手足被毒打至重傷都唔敢求醫，大量骨折義士、柳爺、甩底褲女仔、爆眼少女、救人甩門牙義士，被黑警插贓嫁禍被毒打至腦出血嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n付國豪你收皮啦，瞓幾個鐘仲笑笑口出嚟接受訪問收花<br />\n瘀少少就懶可憐做民族英雄，醜唔醜呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvwP3MD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvwP3MD.jpg&h=bf3b1ed1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d3f4b593624ed0c763d97394eccfedaceee2334","tid":1471800,"uid":81264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66b978f2e5edf70c7d597ba8837a9f3f2b0307c","tid":1471800,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6715d6346ffd1aa3205d56b1b34b67e91f42c44d","tid":1471800,"uid":21399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:16:08.000Z","msg":"我地同你一樣咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e756f5ad891f9faccbcbd1adff733ef8efc33378","tid":1471800,"uid":210677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e9cb84243ec81064bd74fc53dce5b47f0649988","tid":1471800,"uid":36008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>對家陣營真係老閪都唔割<br />\n中排林鄭死攬<br />\n後排支共撐腰<br />\n<br />\n我哋老閪都唔割！<br />\n團結！團結！團團結！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d8fec07ff0ded0fb7d418923628660c85a94c0f8","tid":1471800,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">政治宣傳目標係大陸人唔係香港人</span>"},{"pid":"6e7e35136ef4566aa899cb8a2a2174d263ec6d9a","tid":1471800,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:17:31.000Z","msg":"左膠出來睇下咩叫暴力"},{"pid":"a8d4a9c2e7d8da4e0fc0ce164547528691ece68c","tid":1471800,"uid":104917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:17:34.000Z","msg":"我睇咗<br />\n真係好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry